{"tid":355613,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Minecraft] 1.11.2 模組伺服器 刀劍，冒險，魔法！","createTime":"2017-08-11T12:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T12:48:49.000Z","uid":86943,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2f53d9b9537bf50e6d04f8edf4084f44c00e15b3","tid":355613,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"就咁嘅，我整咗個模組伺服器<br />\n<br />\n而家嚟講仲係好初步，spawn呀，壓力測試呀全部未做，所以想搵下有興趣嘅巴絲打幫手起嘢／鳩fing／試bug<br />\n模組入面有大量建築系玩家資源，甚至可以自己製造新建材<br />\n武器可以儲經驗值增加攻擊力或者解鎖特殊能力<br />\nPVE方面初期有隨機生成嘅地下城，每個地下城有3+層，越向下就越難，入面有特別道具係出面搵唔到嘅<br />\n而且仲有寵物可以捉添<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/174651_3c6e24b5192f12beec3c57286ecb039a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F174651_3c6e24b5192f12beec3c57286ecb039a.png&h=315e03a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/221811_115d292475f99a47c520fe8a03c67f94.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F221811_115d292475f99a47c520fe8a03c67f94.png&h=30a2f370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/030528_6d449cfa4cf846e98075fdfd038aad8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F030528_6d449cfa4cf846e98075fdfd038aad8a.png&h=01554472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/205845_588182a5ab9b6913f89795a89d213cba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F205845_588182a5ab9b6913f89795a89d213cba.png&h=d25d7a5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d52f3eef10667a00a7f7ae55877ec372c7a6441d","tid":355613,"uid":53224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:34:09.000Z",