D&h=500ee78c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B4sQKFH5-ov_c1NTRVhXVTN1aUk</a></blockquote><br />\n諗唔到點解deco craft"},{"pid":"cd96d32dfbc3ff3c861c69a220dfafedebe48010","tid":355613,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"諗唔到點解decocraft會出事，你試下重裝，我去睇下哩個crash 可唔可以recreate"},{"pid":"58cf5f6f44dbe91d94988f15b8e4da8aab3aabb5","tid":355613,"uid":71144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:35:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗唔到點解decocraft會出事，你試下重裝，我去睇下哩個crash 可唔可以recreate</blockquote><br />\n都係就咁安裝完<br />\n將mod 成個放入.minecaft file 入面<br />\n之後開設定 選番 forge  同改左6G ram<br />\n入到game  去左load mod 畫面就跳出"},{"pid":"f542cfdaab3f47893c48b56738caaf4ac54ab842","tid":355613,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:36:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗唔到點解decocraft會出事，你試下重裝，我去睇下哩個crash 可唔可以recreate</blockquote><br />\n都係就咁安裝完<br />\n將mod 成個放入.minecaft file 入面<br />\n之後開設定 選番 forge  同改左6G ram<br />\n入到game  去左load mod 畫面就跳出</blockquote><br />\n你轉用technic platform啦，舊版好多問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頭post有link"},{"pid":"0e13ed83b008c9a8f31c08b5a5027babae24842c","tid":355613,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:43:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dac2ec216635653eae2e9945e60df50dcb4958d","tid":355613,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262bd297a41972aafbacaba112da7d88a7dcfdf3","tid":355613,"uid":65765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:48:57.000Z","msg":"load 晒 2/7 就彈左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces